Properties.Caption: Просмотр прогноза доходов
Properties.Tag: Select [DOC].[CDOC] As [Документ], [DOC].[DDOC] As [Дата документа], Max([Apps_Groups].[GroupCaption]) As [Наименование группы], [CPL_D].[ADM] As [АДМ], Max([K_UL].[NUL]) As [Наименование распорядителя], RTrim([K_D].[CDS]) As [Статья доходов], Max([K_D].[NS]) As [Наименование статьи доходов], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_01])/1000 As [01 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_02])/1000 As [02 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_03])/1000 As [03 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_04])/1000 As [04 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_05])/1000 As [05 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_06])/1000 As [06 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_07])/1000 As [07 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_08])/1000 As [08 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_09])/1000 As [09 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_10])/1000 As [10 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_11])/1000 As [11 месяц], Sum([CPL_D].[SUMM_12])/1000 As [12 месяц] From ((((([CPL_D] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([CPL_D].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Inner Join [K_BD] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[K_BDID]=[K_BD].[K_BDID])) Inner Join [Apps_Groups] With (NoLock) On ([DOC].[Apps_GroupsID]=[Apps_Groups].[Apps_GroupsID])) Inner Join [K_D] With (NoLock) On ([CPL_D].[K_DID]=[K_D].[K_DID])) Left Join [K_UL] With (NoLock) On ([K_D].[K_ULID]=[K_UL].[K_ULID])) Where [K_D].[K_BKID]=26 And [K_D].[CDS] Like '1 [0-9][0-9] [0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9] [0-9][0-9] [0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9] [0-9][0-9][0-9]'  And [DOC].[K_TDID]=86 And |0 Group by [DOC].[CDOC], [DOC].[DDOC], [Apps_Groups].[GroupName], [CPL_D].[ADM], RTrim([K_D].[CDS]) Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр прогноза доходов
